structure_for_AI_to_understand: FundsJSON: Root object with funds array and optional metadata (sources, lastUpdated)
Fund: Contains fundCode (4-5 digit string), fundName (string), fundGroup (string), and fundDescription (string)
Fund Groups: Governmental Cost Funds, Special Revenue Funds, Transportation Funds, Bond Funds, Federal Funds, Other Funds
Fund Codes: Unique identifiers as strings to preserve leading zeros (e.g., '0001' for General Fund)
Data Source: Extracted from budget text files and vendor transaction data
Usage: Referenced in budget allocations and vendor transactions by fundCode
Processing: New funds added when found in budget/vendor data, existing fund names updated if different
